                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature grapples the Foresworn or Strikes him with an unarmed or melee weapon without the reach trait</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> Barbs tangle the triggering creature's attacking limb, and it must attempt a @Check[reflex|dc:30] save. On a failure, it must attempt a @Check[flat|dc:5] to move away from the Foresworn. On a critical failure, this flat check increases to DC 10.</p>"
