                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The graveknight unleashes a @Template[cone|distance:30] of energy. Creatures in the area take @Damage[20d4[electricity]|traits:area-damage] for a creature of the graveknight's level with a @Check[reflex|dc:33|basic|options:area-effect].</p>\n<p>The graveknight can use this ability once every [[/gmr 1d4 #Recharge Devastating Blast]] rounds.</p>"
